One week of loving you Peanut 💙 and one week of watching @capt_eboles grow into the perfect daddy. My heart bursts every time I see you two together. You were made for this 💙

Newborn photos by the talented @feedlebeephotography 💙 our hearts are so full! 

This recliner holds a special place in our hearts, my parents purchased this chair when I was born 33 years ago to rock me to sleep. It has now been moved to our house after 33 years of constant use and will now be used for years to come with our baby girl 💙

✨friends for life ✨

Seriously don’t know what I would do without these ladies💙 our short few years of friendship has grown and changed so much and God gave us all sweet angels at the same time knowing we would need each other to lean on. 

Having your best friends by your side during pregnancy is a dream come true and a true blessing from God. The most unplanned things in life can truly be the biggest blessings 💙

We survived the Rosemont marathon! 

5 action packed events and we only had 1 roll over and 1 missed competition due to a failed water pump. 

Altho the fan judging did not reflect the driving. I Made it to the finals in racing 3 times, was pushed out of my comfort zone with a new event format and managed to get a couple of solid 2 wheel skills hits. And had some solid freestyle runs! 

Shoutout to @logan_vessels for keeping my puppy running and pushing me to drive harder. I figured after a year and a half out of the truck I would be a little rusty but we came back swingin! 🔥💪🏻

#monsterjam #monstermuttdalmation #princessofcarnage #offroad #chicago #rosemont #allstatearena #badassmomma #monstertrucks

Hampton, Virginia ! 

With a tropical storm postponing some events, it all worked out in our favor on National Daughters Day💙 

Not only was I able to secure my first racing win in years, I also took home the Overall Event Championship with my daughter there to witness it 🥹

Such a surreal moment for me as a momma 💙
and much appreciation to my crew chief @logan_vessels for keeping the pup in top shape all weekend!
